---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Bothy. | hideaway."
  description="Plain-language guidance for adults navigating complex financial forms. No jargon, no judgment."
>
  <div class="solution-page">

    <div class="solution-header">
      <div class="solution-header-inner">
        <div class="solution-tag">Made by Laura</div>
        <h1>Bothy.</h1>
        <p class="solution-strapline">
          Plain-language guidance for adults navigating complex financial decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="solution-body">

      <section class="solution-section">
        <h2>The problem it solves</h2>
        <p>
          Financial forms are written for people who already understand the system. Pension
          transfers, beneficiary nominations, fund switches — the language assumes knowledge
          most people don't have, and the stakes are high enough that getting it wrong matters.
        </p>
        <p>
          People find themselves facing important decisions with no one to ask, no plain explanation,
          and no way to tell if they're doing the right thing. So they either guess, delay, or pay
          for advice they can't afford.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="solution-section">
        <h2>What Bothy does</h2>
        <p>
          Bothy explains financial forms in plain language — without jargon, without judgment, and
          without selling anything. It meets you at the form you're looking at and walks you through
          what each section actually means and what you need to do.
        </p>
        <p>
          It doesn't give financial advice. It gives you the understanding you need to make your
          own decisions confidently.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="solution-highlight">
        <blockquote>
          "I finally understood what I was signing. That hadn't happened before."
        </blockquote>
        <cite>— Bothy user, pension transfer review</cite>
      </div>

      <section class="solution-section">
        <h2>Where it started</h2>
        <p>
          The idea came from watching someone I knew stare at a pension transfer form for twenty
          minutes and then put it in a drawer. The form wasn't unusually complicated. The problem
          was that the language assumed they already understood how pensions worked. They didn't.
          Most people don't.
        </p>
        <p>
          Bothy is currently focused on pension transfers — a decision that affects millions of
          people and is often made with too little information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="solution-section">
        <h2>What's next</h2>
        <p>
          The pension transfer focus is a starting point, not a ceiling. The same problem — forms
          written for insiders, decisions made by outsiders — shows up across financial services.
          Bothy is being built to expand.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="solution-cta">
        <h3>Interested in Bothy?</h3>
        <p>
          If you're working on financial services accessibility, or if you've got a specific use
          case in mind, get in touch.
        </p>
        <a href="/subscribe" class="btn-primary">Stay in the loop</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .solution-page {
    padding-top: 5rem;
  }

  .solution-header {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 5rem 3rem 4rem;
  }

  .solution-header-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .solution-tag {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .solution-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #E8F547;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .solution-strapline {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .solution-body {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 3rem 6rem;
  }

  .solution-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .solution-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .solution-section p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }

  .solution-highlight {
    background: var(--stone);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .solution-highlight blockquote {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .solution-highlight cite {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: #6b6254;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .solution-cta {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .solution-cta h3 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .solution-cta p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .solution-header {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    }

    .solution-body {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }

    .solution-highlight {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
